Wiper has a Senate and four MP aspirants in Migori, an ODM zone. The five are said to be afraid of shambolic primaries in ODM.Wiper nominated MCA Richard Wambura, who coordinates the party affairs in the county, said ODM tickets have already been decided on for some MP seats.Ford Kenya county chairman Samuel Migore (above) said opposition parties want to capitalise on ODM s shambolic primaries to capture seats.